    • Constructor Detail

      • DefaultFlagSyntax

        public DefaultFlagSyntax(boolean useEndOfFlags,
                         boolean useEndOfFlagArgs,
                         DefaultFlagSyntax.StrictnessMode unknownLongFlagBehavior,
                         DefaultFlagSyntax.StrictnessMode unknownShortFlagBehavior)
        Parameters:
        useEndOfFlags - whether "--" should be parsed as end of flags mark, and
        useEndOfFlagArgs - whether anything starting with "--" should be treated as end of flag's arguments and not part of them, even when it's not a valid long flag.
        unknownLongFlagBehavior - action to be taken when an unknown long flag is encountered
        unknownShortFlagBehavior - action to be taken when an unknown short flag is encountered
